arm64/cpufeature: Add remaining feature bits in ID_MMFR4 register

Enable all remaining feature bits like EVT, CCIDX, LSM, HPDS, CnP, XNX,
SpecSEI in ID_MMFR4 register per ARM DDI 0487F.a.

